snippet.title: Front Page Sports: Baseball Pro '96 Season (PC) - Intro
snippet.description:
The intro cinematic to the Windows 3x game, Front Page Sports: Baseball Pro '96 Season. 

I don't know why the game has its own fake window inside of the normal Windows window, but it does.
